              <fn id="clcn7.TF.1.1">
                <label>1. </label>
                <p>ARO = infantile malignant autosomal <italic toggle="yes">CLCN7</italic>-related autosomal recessive osteopetrosis</p>
              </fn>
              <fn id="clcn7.TF.1.2">
                <label>2. </label>
                <p>IAO = intermediate autosomal osteopetrosis</p>
              </fn>
              <fn id="clcn7.TF.1.3">
