              <fn id="clcn7.TF.1.4">
                <label>4. </label>
                <p>Generalized osteosclerosis, club-shaped long bones, sclerosis of the skull base, bone-within-bone appearance</p>
              </fn>
              <fn id="clcn7.TF.1.5">
                <label>5. </label>
                <p>Findings similar to ARO, already present in early childhood, but less severe</p>
