                <p>Findings include:  &#x02022;&#x000a0;Osteosclerosis of the spine ("sandwich vertebrae")  &#x02022;&#x000a0;Bone within bone appearance, mainly in iliac wings  &#x02022;&#x000a0;Erlenmeyer-shaped femoral metaphysis  &#x02022;&#x000a0;Mild osteosclerosis of the skull base  &#x02022;&#x000a0;Transverse bands of osteosclerosis in long bones</p>
              </fn>
